// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0626 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 248e7b1c-8ba8-5002-9e85-3679f2870785

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:1*" or process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*photon os:4.0*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*")
